[Civ. No. 3994. Third Appellate District. November 14, 1929.] LESLIE LEE BURR, Respondent, v. WESTERN STATES LIFE INSURANCE COMPANY,-Appellant.

*793T. G. Crothers and M. H. Iverson for Appellant.

Hale MeCowen, Jr., for Respondent.

THE CUURT.

On the authority of McKenzie v. Los Angeles Life Ins. Co. et al., 88 Cal. App. 259 [263 Pac. 338], the petition for a writ of supersedeas is hereby denied.
